data.description: Perfect home for entertaining. This country living home on 1.3 acres offers a large backyard with a pool, tiki bar and coy pond. This 1600 sq. ft. home has a beautiful eat-in kitchen complete with all appliances to stay. A 4 season sun room that overlooks the fenced in backyard. a 3 car garage for all the toys and cars. Basement has an extra shower and possible canning room. A newer reverse osmosis water filtration system and new hot water tank. The list goes on and on.
